headline: MANKIND WARNED OF ITS EXTINCTION; Birth Control Parley Is Told of Over population That Is Depleting Vital Resources
snippet: Ruthless competition is threatening the human race with extinction, a national birth control conference was told here yesterday.

headline: JAPAN POPULATION LAGS; Birth Control Slows Gains-- 100,000,000 Unlikely Soon
snippet: TOKYO, Feb. 25--The popularization of birth control has so slowed the population increase in Japan that census officials now believe the total will not reach the 100,000,000 mark before 1972 or 1973, they said today.
